FBXICT_All: Import all fbx content: geometry, skinning and weights.
FBXICT_Geometry: Import the skeletal mesh geometry only (will create a default skeleton, or map the geometry to the existing one). Morph and LOD can be imported with it.
FBXICT_SkinningWeights: Import the skeletal mesh skinning and weights only (no geometry will be imported). Morph and LOD will not be imported with this settings.
